<section id="emergence" class="emergence-section">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Zone A: Title + Subtitle + Thesis -->
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Emergence</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="emergence-subtitle"><em>What rises when no one gives the orders.</em></p>
    <p class="emergence-thesis">
      Every agent framework has a brain at the top. A planner. An orchestrator. Something that decides who does what and watches them do it. Abjects has no brain. It has a shared pool, the TupleSpace, where tasks appear like spores. Agents don't receive assignments. They watch. They recognize work they know how to do. They claim it. No dispatcher. No scheduler. No single point of failure. Just objects, watching the dark, reaching for what calls to them.
    </p>

    <!-- Zone B: Two Diagrams -->
    <div class="diagrams">
      <div class="diagram-old">
        <h3 class="diagram-label">The Old Way</h3>
        <svg class="diagram-svg diagram-svg-old" viewBox="0 0 620 170" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <defs>
            <marker id="em-arrow-dim" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="10" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto">
              <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#5a5a70"/>
            </marker>
            <marker id="em-arrow-dim-rev" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="0" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto">
              <path d="M 10 0 L 0 5 L 10 10 z" fill="#5a5a70"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>
          <!-- Orchestrator -->
          <rect x="230" y="10" width="160" height="38" rx="6" fill="#12121e" stroke="rgba(255,77,106,0.3)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <text x="310" y="34" text-anchor="middle" fill="#e0e0ea" font-size="13" font-family="monospace">Orchestrator</text>
          <!-- Arrows down -->
          <line x1="260" y1="48" x2="130" y2="80" stroke="#5a5a70" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#em-arrow-dim)"/>
          <text x="175" y="60" fill="#5a5a70" font-size="9" font-family="monospace" opacity="0.6">assigns</text>
          <line x1="310" y1="48" x2="310" y2="80" stroke="#5a5a70" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#em-arrow-dim)"/>
          <text x="328" y="60" fill="#5a5a70" font-size="9" font-family="monospace" opacity="0.6">assigns</text>
          <line x1="360" y1="48" x2="490" y2="80" stroke="#5a5a70" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#em-arrow-dim)"/>
          <text x="445" y="60" fill="#5a5a70" font-size="9" font-family="monospace" opacity="0.6">assigns</text>
          <!-- Workers -->
          <rect x="60" y="85" width="130" height="34" rx="6" fill="#12121e" stroke="#1a1a2a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="125" y="107" text-anchor="middle" fill="#5a5a70" font-size="13" font-family="monospace">Worker A</text>
          <rect x="245" y="85" width="130" height="34" rx="6" fill="#12121e" stroke="#1a1a2a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="310" y="107" text-anchor="middle" fill="#5a5a70" font-size="13" font-family="monospace">Worker B</text>
          <rect x="430" y="85" width="130" height="34" rx="6" fill="#12121e" stroke="#1a1a2a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="495" y="107" text-anchor="middle" fill="#5a5a70" font-size="13" font-family="monospace">Worker C</text>
          <!-- Reports back (dim upward arrows) -->
          <line x1="130" y1="85" x2="265" y2="48" stroke="#5a5a70" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#em-arrow-dim)"/>
          <line x1="310" y1="85" x2="310" y2="48" stroke="#5a5a70" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#em-arrow-dim)"/>
          <line x1="490" y1="85" x2="355" y2="48" stroke="#5a5a70" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#em-arrow-dim)"/>
          <!-- Caption -->
          <text x="310" y="150" text-anchor="middle" fill="#5a5a70" font-size="11" font-family="monospace" font-style="italic" opacity="0.6">one brain, many hands, one point of failure</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="diagram-new">
        <h3 class="diagram-label diagram-label-new">The Inversion</h3>
        <svg class="diagram-svg diagram-svg-new" viewBox="0 0 620 310" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <defs>
            <filter id="em-glow-green">
              <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="blur"/>
